Commentary Text: Siraj to Glenn Phillips, out Caught by Parnell!! What an over this is from Siraj. Just the 4 off it and a wicket. But Glenn Phillips is reviewing this for height. A short of length delivery on the stumps, he swings it straight to the fielder at deep backward square leg. Parnell makes no mistake. This is at the chest and it's a fair delivery. SRH end on 186. Commentary Text: Nitish Reddy to du Plessis, no ball, What drama! That's an excellent catch! But it's a no-ball. Is it a game changer? Another life for Faf. That was short, du Plessis went for the pull and hammered it. Dagar came in from deep mid, the ball was dying on him and that too very quickly. He managed to gulp it down.
